commit.title: Closes #7699 (confusing undocumented multi-class syntax of "Bind Scope").
commit.message:
Closes #7699 (confusing undocumented multi-class syntax of "Bind Scope").

Only "Bind Scope a_scope with class" is documented. Do not provide
"Bind Scope a_scope with class1 .. classn" as it is a source of
confusion. Think e.g. as "Bind Scope b_scope with option nat".
